# Setting up and editing your channel

You can view and edit your channel by clicking on the ‘My Channel’ tab on the Dashboard.

**Step 1.** Press the **menu** button on either controller to open the **main menu**. Then click on the **Dashboard** button.

[INSERT VISUAL]

**Step 2.** Click on the **My Channel** tab on the Dashboard and click **Edit Channel Info**.

**Step 3.** Enter or edit your photo, channel name and channel description. Save your changes.

[INSERT VISUAL]

> **Note:** You can also edit your channel info through the Creator Portal website.

